description:
Cooking smoke isn’t just about smell, it’s about air quality.

In this video, I push the Arspura 36” IQV Smart Range Hood to the limit by testing it with indoor BBQ smoke, extreme suction scenarios, and real-time PM2.5 air quality measurements.

No spec-sheet talk, just a real stress test to see how fast it clears smoke, how strong the suction really is, and how well it improves kitchen air quality.
